<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email</title>
    <style>
        body, html {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin:  auto;
            height: 70%;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 0;
        }

        .header h1, .header h3 {
            font-weight: lighter;
            margin: 0;
            margin-left: 12%;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            padding: 20px;
            height: 80%;
            position: relative;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-left: 10%;
            margin-right: 10%;
            text-align: justify;
        }

    

        .confirmation {
            margin-top: 10%;
            margin-left: 10%;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #0057D9;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex; /* Enable flexbox for the button */
            align-items: center; /* Align content vertically within the button */
        }
        
        .btn img {
            margin-right: 10px; /* Add a margin to space the image and text */
        }

        .additional-text {
            text-align: justify;
            margin-left: 10%;
            margin-right: 10%;
            margin-top: 8%;
            color: #000;
        }

        .additional-text2 {
            margin-left: 10%;
            margin-right: 10%;
            margin-top: 15%;
        }
        .additional-text3 {
            text-align: left;  
        }.additional-text4 {
            text-align: right;  
        }.text-container {
            font-size: 0.8em;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center; /* This aligns content vertically within the container */
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding:  0 10px;
        }

    </style>
    
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>HR HUB</h1>
            <h3>Vendor Management</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>HR HUB'a hoşgeldiniz. Kullanıcı şifrenizi belirlemek için aşağıdaki butona tıklayınız ve Vendor Management'ı Keşfetmeye Başlayın.</p>
            <div class="confirmation">
            <form action="<%= apiPort %>/api/company/accept" method="POST">
                <input type="hidden" name="companyName" value="<%= companyName %>"> 
                <input type="hidden" name="email" value="<%=email%>">
            <button type="submit" class="btn">
              <img src="../icons/Vector.png" alt="Button image description" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;">Katıl</button>
          </form>
            </div>
            <p class="additional-text">Eğer bu mailin yanlış geldiğini düşünüyorsanız Lütfen Dikkate Almayınız</p>
        </div >

        
    </div>

</body>
</html>